description: This easy stir-fry recipe made with honey soy beef and crunchy cashews is so quick to make and perfect for midweek dinners. All you need is four ingredients!
keywords: Stir-fry,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Egg free,Low sugar,Beef,Fakeaway,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Rice,Dinner Made Easy,Dairy free
name: Easy Honey Soy Beef & Cashew Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 550g Cook stir-fry kit with honey soy sauce sachet

recipeInstructions.text: Heat 2 tbs peanut oil in a wok or large frying pan over high heat. Stir-fry beef, in batches, for 2 minutes or until browned and almost cooked through. Transfer to a bowl. Cover to keep warm.
Cook stir-fry kit according to packet instructions, adding beef and 1/4 cup cashews when adding sauce mixture to pan. Toss to combine. Cook for 2 minutes or until coated and warmed through.
Heat rice according to packet instructions.
Serve stir-fry over rice topped with remaining cashews.
